    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, offering a refined balance of performance and long-term value. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our dealership\u2019s exacting standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic presentation. Accompanied by a consistent service history, this vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver seeking a dependable, high-caliber automotive investment. Professional-grade quality meets uncompromising reliability.",
      "price": 36800.0,
