      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag. The exterior retains a deep, glossy finish with only minor road-wear consistent with careful ownership. Inside, the cabin remains smoke-free and crisp, featuring supple seating and fully functional technology interfaces. Mechanically, the car is sound; it has been serviced at regular intervals, with recent maintenance updates ensuring it's ready for the road today. It handles with precision and provides a quiet, comfortable ride. Perfect for a discerning buyer looking for a dependable, stylish, and high-performing vehicle that has been treated with genuine care.",
      "price": 34500.0,
