    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it the perfect dependable choice for someone who wants a smooth drive without the brand-new price tag. Everything is running great and it\u2019s ready for a new home! I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will enjoy it as much as I have\u2014feel free to reach out if you want to come see it!",
