      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound BMW E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies. This unit retains its tactile Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, providing a direct mechanical connection often lost in modern counterparts. The chassis is robust, having undergone professional rear subframe reinforcement\u2014a critical preventative measure for this platform. The dual-VANOS variable valve timing system has been recently serviced to ensure precise cam phasing and optimal torque delivery across the rev range. While the exterior shows minor stone chips and patina consistent with enthusiast use, the performance envelope remains intact, supported by a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential and a crisp, responsive suspension setup.",
